{"tid":1939312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好多人錯誤利用加速主義","createTime":"2020-03-23T05:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T15:26:05.000Z","uid":19945,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e0e7b0fac2190bc86e315ff0cb51f4834df525cc","tid":1939312,"uid":19945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T05:29:51.000Z","msg":"首先多謝咁多位巴打國際戰線幫手<br />\n成效愈來愈好<br />\n基本上就連左膠個邊都開始轉去鬧中共不鬧中國<br />\n但近日見到好多連登post唔知係咪太興奮<br />\n開post諗住組織扮小粉紅行動<br />\n仲諗埋hashtag叫人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加速主義係唔洗推<br />\n亦唔應該用香港人名義推<br />\n你想撥火我教你點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">直接自己開個account同小粉紅互follow</span></strong></span><br />\n再不斷增加實力聯合白左<br />\n你有心嘅大概經營一星期就可以有個千人follow嘅account<br />\n到時你直接自製hashtag再叫班友班手<br />\n好快就撥到火<br />\n<br />\n從來離間同臥底都係低調<br />\n邊有人大大聲話自己臥底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後不論你用咩方式<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">開Twitter呀屌你</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d8606b2ee3f58cbdfb5b18d46ed5c7bba504bd42","tid":1939312,"uid":20231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T05:30:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20bc92a04ce1acb291b7c5e608bd1ad3ad50acc8","tid":1939312,"uid":19945,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T05:33:10.000Z","msg":"其實小粉紅好易connect<br />\n你講咩佢都會幫手<br />\n仲要最鐘意人身攻擊<br />\n基本上最倒米嘅嘢<br />\n佢地最興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac3c1b762f7d51f5c026aa702e220eebe62ef06","tid":1939312,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T05:34:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"625e984e2a19bd084d9fe7b63ebc32d372145c47","tid":1939312,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20bc92a0